oads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 8 月 23 日，Catfish and the Bottlemen 乐队的 Van McCann 在 2024 年利兹音乐节第一天在英国利兹布拉默姆公园的主舞台上表演。图片来源：马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（8 月 23 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">，Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>成为利兹音乐节的头条新闻。这是他们玩过的所有内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3785825">Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 直播博客：所有发生的动作</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-six-headliners-revealed-as-first-wave-of-line-up-announced-tickets-3548085">第二次成为雷丁和利兹音乐节的主角</a>，并将于明天（8 月 25 日星期日）晚上 8:10 在雷丁的主舞台上演出。</p><p>在周末最受期待的表演之一中，主唱范·麦肯 (Van McCann) 为歌迷带来了一张包含三张专辑中热门歌曲的歌单，让歌迷们大饱眼福。威尔士乐队以《Longshot》拉开了他们的演出序幕，随后是《Kathleen》和《Soundcheck》。</p><p>随后，他们演奏了《Twice》、《Homesick》和《Outside》，然后带领歌迷合唱了取自 2016 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-catfish-and-the-bottlemen-16481-305848">The Ride</a> 》的《7》，充满活力。播放的大部分曲目来自他们 2014 年的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-15657-324542">Balcony</a> 》，包括更接近的歌曲《Cocoon》</p><p>请查看下面的曲目列表和他们的表演片段。</p><h3> <strong>Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen&#39;s 利兹音乐节 2024 年曲目列表为：</strong></h3><p> <strong>“远射”</strong><br /> <strong>“凯瑟琳”</strong><br /> <strong>“声音检查”</strong><br /> <strong>“奶嘴”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;两次&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;掉出来&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;对话&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;想家&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“2全部”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;兰戈&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;外部&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;波动&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>‘7’</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;茧&#39;</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">鲶鱼和装瓶商今天在利兹唱茧<br />我很激动<a href="https://t.co/jSQij92lkq">pic.twitter.com/jSQij92lkq</a></p><p> — 玛哈 |看到乔斯特!!!.€:):) <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26bd.png" alt="⚽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f54a.png" alt="🕊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@waveyfingdavey） <a href="https://twitter.com/waveyfingdavey/status/1827087262557073561?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 23 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">利兹音乐节上的CATB！！！ <a href="https://t.co/CjkjVMePe0">pic.twitter.com/CjkjVMePe0</a></p><p> - 鲶鱼和装瓶工档案 (@catbfiles) <a href="https://twitter.com/catbfiles/status/1827079584661000683?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 23 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" ti